{"tid":2116204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人成日覺得抗疫可以比得上台灣？","createTime":"2020-07-20T04:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T04:26:12.000Z","uid":253501,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2294e365ca02859d567bb1a8ece2345730c6e0b5","tid":2116204,"uid":253501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎都已經有咗半年,台灣最後一波已經係4月嘅事,到6月開始已經淨係喺公共交通工具上面要戴口罩。由其他國家嚟嘅人強制由專車送去防疫旅館隔離14日,然後再自主隔離（唔俾番工番學）7日。香港個邊境措施做得差,市民嘅抗疫意識又唔係特別好,疫情一直反反覆覆,好似唔會完咁。"},{"pid":"f8807d97ef935f5b213e63319e0c6abf44952d06","tid":2116204,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"大佬啲policy係政府定架<br />\n關我哋撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c13b9ec093768ad16a9dd2beba28433d67830b","tid":2116204,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"搞清楚先，唔係香港人成日覺得可以比得上台灣<br />\n而係香港政府成日覺得可以比得上台灣"},{"pid":"974c8220b05f89f24ed08c0016edadddf3f30603","tid":2116204,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"一日唔封關，<br />\n香港人做到識飛都無用。"},{"pid":"2eeb31ef8f6540bf861f830aae05b91106d1d1b8","tid":2116204,"uid":253501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"唉,再搞唔掂可能要大學畢業先番到香港"},{"pid":"2ee478b48aee560bbd1c4576b09402bd60afe506","tid":2116204,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:23:39.000Z","msg":"幾時有覺得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f7af2327bd9ce1935872f1a2744d03e6debf61","tid":2116204,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"背靠大國，有一打肺都唔夠用啦"},{"pid":"e588a0d96f67efabb5174b62540fe2c567492c96","tid":2116204,"uid":109086,"like":0,"di